message.body: I don't know if you heard but fyi I am not your neighbor anymore, now I live here: ï¿¼

Right next to the mouth of the wissahickon at the end of Kelly drive. Extremely accessible by bike, my commute to penn is beautiful and ~30 mins. Also a train at the end of the street. Telling you all this so you visit me.
I am getting my plans together to clear the big yard so I can have a biiiig garden and keep bees, etc

House warming cocktail party in December.

So weird for me not to live in west philly so I am really into the idea of people visiting.
